- Created CloudWatch log group **/aws/cloudtrail/jayknowso-audit**  
- Created IAM role **jayknowso-cloudtrail-cloudwatch-role** with least-privilege write policy  
- Wired CloudTrail to stream logs to CloudWatch  
- Created metric filter for root account API calls  
- Created alarm **jayknowso-root-account-usage-alarm** (threshold=1, period=300s)  
- 5-test CLI proof documented  
- ADR-007 written and committed  
**Phase 2 CLOSED**

